name: Tammyhembrow - Textual Inversion
description:
This ti was requested by my fellow ti creator, friend and person I enjoy talking to, @JernauGurgeh.

Tammy, or tammyhembrow on instagram, is an instagram model and fitness advocate with over 16 million followers.

First time doing a ti soley on instagram pictures. I hope you enjoy this ti as much as I do!

Still learning and improving the progress of the training, any feedback is welcome.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
